de.thkoeln.bibl.api.media

Class LibraryMedia<T extends AbstractMediaNumber>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.media.LibraryMedia<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of media number the library media used
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LibraryMedia<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SisisMedia

    public class LibraryMedia<T extends AbstractMediaNumber>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LibraryMedia<T>>
    Class implements the structure of a library media and extends the media number by other media related data. This class supports the serializing to/from XML data.
    Author:
    Patrick Rogalla
